=A Flower On The Continent=

2
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:38,660
=Episode 6=

3
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:39,600
Tell me now!

4
00:00:40,360 --> 00:00:41,160
Ning Xuanzhou!

5
00:00:41,480 --> 00:00:42,080
Xiyu!

6
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:55,320
You beast from Ning!

7
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:08,040
She infiltrated the teahouse
with malicious intent.

8
00:01:08,100 --> 00:01:09,040
I was defending myself.

9
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:12,760
Explain clearly.

10
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:14,600
I thought you wouldn't listen.

11
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:20,520
The men in black who tried to kill you
in the alley

12
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,880
also used this device.

13
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:24,200
Yes, they belonged to the same group.

14
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:25,960
I was bored and came here for tea,

15
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,760
but they had set up an ambush.

16
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:34,800
Ruyi said she lived in a small village
near the Yan border.

17
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:37,440
Dissatisfied with the Ning army's raids,

18
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,600
she fled to the capital.

19
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:42,160
I never expected
she was actually from Ning.

20
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,040
From Ning?

21
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:53,360
You once placed one of these on the desk

22
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,200
in the academy,

23
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:56,340
saying you brought it from home
for self-defense.

24
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:59,840
This group uses Ning's specialties.

25
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,160
Aren't they from Ning?

26
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,480
(If she knew I suspected her,)

27
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,840
(she'd be furious.)

28
00:02:06,240 --> 00:02:07,200
You make a good point.

29
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,960
From this, we can deduce

30
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:11,190
the spies inciting war
between the two countries

31
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,680
are hidden within Ning.

32
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:14,400
Not necessarily.

33
00:02:15,260 --> 00:02:16,660
There might be spies in both sides.

34
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,960
But it's likely more in Ning,

35
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,320
given they even use your...

36
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:21,760
Watch out!

37
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,640
Luckily, it was soaked in water.

38
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:25,720
Otherwise, you'd be hurt.

39
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:28,800
A man shouldn't fear getting hurt.

40
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,360
Your hand...

41
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,000
It's nothing.

42
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,400
A man shouldn't fear getting hurt.

43
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,280
You're different.

44
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,160
How different?

45
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:47,720
You...

46
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:51,640
In my heart,

47
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,640
you'll always be the princess of Ning.

48
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:57,400
What did you say?

49
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:01,280
First impressions really matter.

50
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,240
Does your wound hurt?

51
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:31,640
No.

52
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:35,230
Why are you holding your arm then?

53
00:03:35,300 --> 00:03:36,250
I'll change the bandage.

54
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,080
No need.

55
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:39,200
I'm not a princess.

56
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,640
Still holding a grudge?

57
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:45,640
It's all in the past.

58
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:54,440
Madam Sun reported that day

59
00:03:54,700 --> 00:03:56,280
and the officials took Ruyi's body away.

60
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:57,800
Now there's news.

61
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,800
The coroner has confirmed

62
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:01,880
Ruyi slit her own throat

63
00:04:02,010 --> 00:04:03,260
and it's been ruled as suicide.

64
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,560
But it's strange.

65
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,480
Even if she couldn't kill you,

66
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,560
she could've escaped.

67
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:10,200
Why would she commit suicide?

68
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:12,000
I heard assassins commit suicide

69
