♪In the season when the wind
dances and flutters♪

274
00:13:24,020 --> 00:13:26,500
♪The flourishing brilliance♪

275
00:13:26,780 --> 00:13:29,380
♪Soaks into your affection♪

276
00:13:29,380 --> 00:13:33,620
♪The rivers and mountains stand still♪

277
00:13:34,260 --> 00:13:38,740
♪The years turn, always blooming♪

278
00:13:38,980 --> 00:13:41,900
♪Accompanying like a shadow♪

279
00:13:42,260 --> 00:13:44,620
♪Transforming into my love♪

280
00:13:44,620 --> 00:13:48,620
♪Shining like stars♪

